A former Big Brother Naija housemate, Tacha Akide has expressed her love for Nigerian musician, Tekno. The reality TV star, took to her Twitter account to reveal that she has a soft spot for the ‘Pana’ hit maker. An excited Tacha, taking to her Twitter, wrote Tekno’s name with the love emoji beside it, as an indication of her love for him. She tweeted: “Alhaji TEKNO❤️” This is also as Tekno had in an earlier post, written Tacha’s name with some stressed letters, indicating interest in the reality star or her activities. Source